Meet shy boy Gunner. #A5139347 Gunner is 3 year old pitbull. What he lacks in confidence he makes up for in sweetness.  Gunner needs an adopter who will be patient with him and show him he is safe.  We don‚Äôt know what kind of adventures he had but we are sure it was super scary out there by himself. He is very shy at first but when he gets to know you he comes out of his shell and his tail will start to wag.  Gunner knows his basic commands and is great on a leash. Gunner also lights up when he sees other dogs, so we believe he would be a good addition in a home with other pets. Gunner is a very sweet boy who just needs a little time and love invested into him.

Hello there! I am Sebastian, or you can call me "Seb". I am not just another handsome face trying to make it in La La Land-- I am looking for the real thing! And by that, I mean an awesome, loving, and #furever home!
You might think I'm a natural-born performer with the amount of tricks I know-- Sit, Down, and Shake for starters. But hey, I am well trained! I also like to play fetch and 'work' for treats (what a fun job!). Making people smile is my best skill though -- let's make good times together!
.
Sebastian is a 3 years old, 70 pounds, neutered male. He came into the shelter on March 17, 2017 when his owners surrendered him for "moving". They reported they had him since he was a puppy.
This handsome, connected, and smart boy is ready for a new relationship that will last-- please come meet him today! And don't forget to share! üíó
